<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>LA Day Trip — May 10th</title>
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
    background: #faf9f7;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Header */
  .header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 48px 32px 40px;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    color: #faf9f7;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .header .eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .header h1 {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: normal;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .header .subtitle {
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #aaa;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  /* Section labels */
  .section-label {
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }

  /* Cluster card */
  .cluster {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cluster-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: #f5f4f2;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }

  .cluster-name {
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .cluster-note {
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #888;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  /* Stop rows */
  .stop {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 56px 1fr auto;
    align-items: start;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
  }

  .stop:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .stop-time {
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #888;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding-top: 2px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .stop-info { }

  .stop-name {
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .walk-badge {
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    background: #e8f4e8;
    color: #3a7a3a;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .drive-badge {
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    background: #f0f0f0;
    color: #666;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .stop-detail {
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #888;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .stop-cost {
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    white-space: nowrap;
    text-align: right;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }

  .stop-cost .range {
    display: block;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: #aaa;
    font-weight: normal;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  /* Drive connector */
  .drive-connector {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    margin: -1px 0;
  }

  .drive-line {
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, #ccc 0px, #ccc 4px, transparent 4px, transparent 8px);
  }

  .drive-label {
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #aaa;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* Cost summary */
  .cost-section {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cost-header {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: #f5f4f2;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }

  .cost-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 11px 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .cost-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .cost-row .label { color: #444; }
  .cost-row .label small { display: block; color: #aaa; font-size: 10px; margin-top: 1px; }
  .cost-row .amount { font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a; }

  .cost-row.total {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    color: #faf9f7;
  }
  .cost-row.total .label { color: #ccc; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .cost-row.total .amount { color: #fff; font-size: 15px; }

  .cost-row.subtotal {
    background: #f5f4f2;
    border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }
  .cost-row.subtotal .label { font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a; }
  .cost-row.subtotal .amount { font-size: 13px; }

  /* Alert */
  .alert {
    background: #fff8e6;
    border: 1px solid #f5d78e;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #7a5c00;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .alert strong { font-weight: 700; }

  /* Logistics */
  .logistics {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .logistics-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .logistics-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .logistics-icon { font-size: 14px; flex-shrink: 0; padding-top: 1px; }
  .logistics-text { color: #444; line-height: 1.5; }
  .logistics-text strong { color: #1a1a1a; font-weight: 600; }

  /* Footer */
  .footer {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #bbb;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding-top: 8px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="header">
    <div class="eyebrow">Girls Trip</div>
    <h1>LA — May 10th</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">5 girls · 8:00 AM → 10:30 PM</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Logistics strip -->
  <div class="section-label">Logistics</div>
  <div class="logistics" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
    <div class="logistics-row">
      <div class="logistics-icon">🚗</div>
      <div class="logistics-text"><strong>BMW rental</strong> — arrives at HMC at 8:00 AM, due back by 10:30 PM. $180 total = <strong>$36/person</strong>.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="logistics-row">
      <div class="logistics-icon">🅿️</div>
      <div class="logistics-text"><strong>Park only 3 times in LA.</strong> Silver Lake (free behind Taix), Melrose/Pink Wall (walk entire cluster from here), Oxford Center Plaza Ktown (free lot, walk entire cluster from here).</div>
    </div>
    <div class="logistics-row">
      <div class="logistics-icon">🚶</div>
      <div class="logistics-text"><strong>Walking clusters:</strong> Pink Wall → Community Goods → Erewhon → The Grove are all within ~15 min walk. Out of Ordi → DAMO → Damsot → KazuNori are all within ~10 min walk.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="logistics-row">
      <div class="logistics-icon">⚠️</div>
      <div class="logistics-text"><strong>Kanomwaan closes at 8:30 PM on Sundays.</strong> Must arrive by 7:45 PM — this is the tightest constraint of the night.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="logistics-row">
      <div class="logistics-icon">📵</div>
      <div class="logistics-text"><strong>No reservations needed anywhere</strong> — every stop is walk-in only. Expect lines at Out of Ordi (~20–30 min) and Damsot (~15–30 min on weekends).</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Itinerary -->
  <div class="section-label">The Itinerary</div>

  <!-- CLUSTER 1 -->
  <div class="cluster">
    <div class="cluster-header">
      <span class="cluster-name">📍 Cluster 1 — Silver Lake</span>
      <span class="cluster-note">Drive 45 min from Claremont</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stop">
      <div class="stop-time">9:30 AM</div>
      <div class="stop-info">
        <div class="stop-name">🛍 Silverlake Flea <span class="drive-badge">Drive</span></div>
        <div class="stop-detail">1911 Sunset Blvd · Free entry · Opens 9:30am Sundays<br>Vintage clothing, jewelry, vinyl, food trucks. ~1 hr.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stop-cost">Free<span class="range">+ whatever<br>you buy</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="drive-connector">
    <div class="drive-line"></div>
    <div class="drive-label">🚗 Drive 15 min → Melrose</div>
    <div class="drive-line"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- CLUSTER 2 -->
  <div class="cluster">
    <div class="cluster-header">
      <span class="cluster-name">📍 Cluster 2 — Melrose / Fairfax</span>
      <span class="cluster-note">Park once on Melrose · Walk everything</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stop">
      <div class="stop-time">11:00 AM</div>
      <div class="stop-info">
        <div class="stop-name">📸 Pink Wall (Paul Smith)</div>
        <div class="stop-detail">8221 Melrose Ave · Anchor point — park here<br>Open 24/7. Photo op, 15 min.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stop-cost">Free</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stop">
      <div class="stop-time">11:20 AM</div>
      <div class="stop-info">
        <div class="stop-name">☕ Community Goods <span class="walk-badge">Walk ~10 min</span></div>
        <div class="stop-detail">710 N Edinburgh Ave · Opens 8am Sundays<br>Famous matcha einspanner, breakfast sliders. Grab to go.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stop-cost">$7–12<span class="range">per person</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="stop">
      <div class="stop-time">11:50 AM</div>
      <div class="stop-info">
        <div class="stop-name">🛒 Erewhon <span class="walk-badge">Walk ~8 min</span></div>
        <div class="stop-detail">7660 Beverly Blvd · Open 7am–11pm<br>The viral smoothies. Budget accordingly lol.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stop-cost">$18–26<span class="range">per smoothie</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="stop">
      <div class="stop-time">12:20 PM</div>
      <div class="stop-info">
        <div class="stop-name">🛍 The Grove + Brandy Melville <span class="walk-badge">Walk ~8 min</span></div>
        <div class="stop-detail">189 The Grove Dr · Opens 11am Sundays (Brandy opens 11am, closes 8pm)<br>The Brandy here has an attached café with pizza + coffee if you want a snack.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stop-cost">Varies<span class="range">shopping</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="drive-connector">
    <div class="drive-line"></div>
    <div class="drive-label">🚗 Drive 15 min → Koreatown</div>
    <div class="drive-line"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- CLUSTER 3 -->
  <div class="cluster">
    <div class="cluster-header">
      <span class="cluster-name">📍 Cluster 3 — Koreatown</span>
      <span class="cluster-note">Park once at Oxford Center Plaza · Walk everything</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stop">
      <div class="stop-time">1:10 PM</div>
      <div class="stop-info">
        <div class="stop-name">🍞 Out of Ordi <span class="drive-badge">Drive</span></div>
        <div class="stop-detail">3524 W 8th St · Opens 11:30am · Closes 3pm<br>Korean salt bread. Weekend limit: 4 pieces/person. Expect 20–30 min line. Eat immediately.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stop-cost">~$16<span class="range">4 pc × ~$4 ea</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="stop">
      <div class="stop-time">1:50 PM</div>
      <div class="stop-info">
        <div class="stop-name">🍵 DAMO Matcha <span class="walk-badge">Walk 1 min</span></div>
        <div class="stop-detail">3510 W 8th St · Same plaza as Out of Ordi<br>Open until 6pm. Get the matcha einspanner. ~15 min wait.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stop-cost">$7–9<span class="range">per drink</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="stop">
      <div class="stop-time">2:20 PM</div>
      <div class="stop-info">
        <div class="stop-name">🍚 Damsot — Lunch <span class="walk-badge">Walk ~10 min</span></div>
        <div class="stop-detail">3377 Wilshire Blvd · Open 11am–3pm for lunch<br>Korean clay pot rice. Each pot comes with banchan, salad, miso soup. No takeout — dine in only. ⚠️ Check in immediately, weekend waits can be 15–30 min.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stop-cost">$19–29<span class="range">per person</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="stop">
      <div class="stop-time">3:30–6 PM</div>
      <div class="stop-info">
        <div class="stop-name">🕰 Free Time — Koreatown</div>
        <div class="stop-detail">Vintage shops, exploring, Ktown malls, rest. Car stays at Oxford Plaza.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stop-cost">—</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stop">
      <div class="stop-time">6:30 PM</div>
      <div class="stop-info">
        <div class="stop-name">🍣 KazuNori — Dinner <span class="walk-badge">Walk ~4 min</span></div>
        <div class="stop-detail">3465 W 6th St · Open until 11pm Sundays<br>Hand roll bar by the Sushi Nozawa Group. No reservations. No tipping — hospitality included in price. Order a set: 3 rolls ($15), 5 rolls ($25), 6 rolls ($28). Get the salmon, toro, and lobster.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stop-cost">$25–35<span class="range">per person</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="drive-connector">
    <div class="drive-line"></div>
    <div class="drive-label">🚗 Drive 15 min → East Hollywood</div>
    <div class="drive-line"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Standalone stops -->
  <div class="cluster">
    <div class="cluster-header">
      <span class="cluster-name">📍 East Hollywood → Diamond Bar → Home</span>
      <span class="cluster-note">Final stretch</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stop">
      <div class="stop-time">7:45 PM</div>
      <div class="stop-info">
        <div class="stop-name">🍨 Kanomwaan Thai Gelato <span class="drive-badge">Drive</span></div>
        <div class="stop-detail">5261 Hollywood Blvd · ⚠️ Closes 8:30pm Sundays — must arrive by 7:45<br>Thai-inspired gelato + shaved ice. The mango sticky rice shaved ice is enormous — share it. Thai tea and pandan gelato are also incredible.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stop-cost">$8–14<span class="range">per person</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="stop">
      <div class="stop-time">9:15 PM</div>
      <div class="stop-info">
        <div class="stop-name">🧋 Torotea <span class="drive-badge">Drive ~35 min</span></div>
        <div class="stop-detail">1395 S Diamond Bar Blvd · Open until 10pm<br>Right off the 57, perfectly on the way home. Popcorn milk tea + brown sugar tapiochi. Then 15 min to Claremont.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stop-cost">$7–10<span class="range">per drink</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="stop">
      <div class="stop-time">10:15 PM</div>
      <div class="stop-info">
        <div class="stop-name">🏁 Back at HMC</div>
        <div class="stop-detail">Car returned by 10:30 PM ✓</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stop-cost">—</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Cost Summary -->
  <div class="section-label" style="margin-top: 32px;">Cost Breakdown Per Person</div>

  <div class="alert">
    <strong>Heads up:</strong> All prices below are estimates based on typical orders. Actual costs will vary based on how many rolls/items you get, whether you share dishes, and how much you spend shopping. Think of this as a realistic floor — you could spend less if you share, or more if you go off-menu. Damsot and KazuNori are the two biggest meals. Everything else is snacks/drinks.
  </div>

  <div class="cost-section">
    <div class="cost-header">
      <div class="section-label" style="margin: 0; border: none; padding: 0;">Fixed Cost</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cost-row">
      <span class="label">🚗 Car rental split 5 ways<small>$180 total BMW rental</small></span>
      <span class="amount">$36</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cost-row subtotal">
      <span class="label">Fixed subtotal</span>
      <span class="amount">$36</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cost-section">
    <div class="cost-header">
      <div class="section-label" style="margin: 0; border: none; padding: 0;">Food & Drinks</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cost-row">
      <span class="label">☕ Community Goods<small>Matcha einspanner or latte</small></span>
      <span class="amount">~$9</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cost-row">
      <span class="label">🛒 Erewhon<small>One smoothie — the whole point of LA</small></span>
      <span class="amount">~$20</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cost-row">
      <span class="label">🍞 Out of Ordi<small>4 pieces of salt bread (weekend max)</small></span>
      <span class="amount">~$16</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cost-row">
      <span class="label">🍵 DAMO Matcha<small>Matcha einspanner</small></span>
      <span class="amount">~$8</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cost-row">
      <span class="label">🍚 Damsot — Lunch<small>One pot rice (includes banchan, salad, miso). Steak pot is $26, eggplant is $19, others $19–29</small></span>
      <span class="amount">~$22</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cost-row">
      <span class="label">🍣 KazuNori — Dinner<small>5-roll set ($25) or 6-roll set ($28). No tipping required — hospitality included</small></span>
      <span class="amount">~$28</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cost-row">
      <span class="label">🍨 Kanomwaan Thai Gelato<small>Mango sticky rice shaved ice or 2 scoops gelato</small></span>
      <span class="amount">~$10</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cost-row">
      <span class="label">🧋 Torotea<small>One drink (popcorn milk tea + tapiochi)</small></span>
      <span class="amount">~$9</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cost-row subtotal">
      <span class="label">Food & drinks subtotal</span>
      <span class="amount">~$122</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cost-section">
    <div class="cost-row total">
      <span class="label">Estimated Total Per Person</span>
      <span class="amount">~$158</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cost-row" style="background: #f5f4f2;">
      <span class="label" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; color: #666;">Budget for shopping, extras, parking tips, etc.<small style="color:#aaa;">Silverlake Flea + The Grove are the main shopping moments</small></span>
      <span class="amount" style="font-size: 12px; color: #888;">+$?</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cost-row">
      <span class="label" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; color: #666;"><strong>Comfortable budget to bring (all-in)</strong></span>
      <span class="amount">$175–200</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Notes -->
  <div class="section-label" style="margin-top: 32px;">Good to Know</div>
  <div class="logistics">
    <div class="logistics-row">
      <div class="logistics-icon">💳</div>
      <div class="logistics-text"><strong>Cash or Venmo for Silverlake Flea vendors.</strong> Cards accepted everywhere else.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="logistics-row">
      <div class="logistics-icon">🍞</div>
      <div class="logistics-text"><strong>Eat the Out of Ordi salt bread immediately</strong> — texture is dramatically better warm. Don't save it for later.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="logistics-row">
      <div class="logistics-icon">🍣</div>
      <div class="logistics-text"><strong>KazuNori doesn't require tipping</strong> — hospitality is included in the price. This is genuinely rare and appreciated.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="logistics-row">
      <div class="logistics-icon">🍽️</div>
      <div class="logistics-text"><strong>Damsot is dine-in only, no takeout.</strong> Check in the moment you arrive — weekend waits are real. Lunch closes at 3pm sharp.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="logistics-row">
      <div class="logistics-icon">🍨</div>
      <div class="logistics-text"><strong>Share the Kanomwaan shaved ice</strong> — it's massive and meant for sharing. The mango sticky rice shaved ice easily feeds 2–3 people.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="logistics-row">
      <div class="logistics-icon">☀️</div>
      <div class="logistics-text"><strong>Wear sunscreen and comfortable shoes.</strong> The Melrose cluster especially is a solid 30-min round-trip walk in May heat.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">Made with love · LA Day Trip · May 10th</div>

</div>
</body>
</html>